::Rodimus Prime::

Rodimus was getting mad. This Predacon had requested the meeting but refused to speak.

&quot;Ok if you dont want to talk, we&#39;ll let you rest.&quot;

Rodimus looks at the guards in his office.
(I cant remember who is in there, it&#39;s been so long since we started this meeting.)

&quot;Guys, take this Predacon to the security cells. I want him held, untill he decides to talk about whatever it is he originally wanted too. Treat him fairly though.&quot;

With that Rodimus gets up and leaves his office. He thinks as he walks, &quot;The office is good but I&#39;ll need to move some of my belongind in there to personalize it.&quot;

Rodimus walks untill he finds Ragnar.

&quot;What was the outcome of the fight?&quot; He asks.

::Kup::

Kup had been waiting for this new bot(Cheetor) to come out fo the CR&#39;s forever and he was tired of waiting. He walked out of the room, and went to the Mess Hall. Kup got himself a glass of Ener-Gin(Alchoholic Energon in human terms) and sat at a table. Maybe someone would join him.

